## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="61fe4-132">此属性以 Y 轴刻度的百分比度量。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61fe4-132">This property is measured as a percentage of the Y-axis scale.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="61fe4-133">默认情况下，其值设置为25。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61fe4-133">By default, its value is set to 25.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="61fe4-134">这意味着，如果序列中的数据点的比例至少为25%，则将使用刻度分隔线进行折叠。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61fe4-134">This means that data points in a series that have a difference of at least 25% of the scale will be collapsed with a scale break.</span></span>  
  
   
  
